Zei,"Oh, it is. According to legend, it was built by the great Knowledge Spirit, Wan Shi Tong, with the help of his ""foxy"" knowledge seekers.",哦，是的。根据传说，它是由伟大的知识精神万世通在他的“狡猾”知识寻求者的帮助下建造的。
