Wan Shi Tong,"Hm! Humans only bother learning things to get the edge on other humans. Like that firebender who came to this place a few years ago, looking to destroy his enemy. So ... who are you trying to destroy?",哼！人类只会费心学习，以获得其他人类的优势。就像几年前来到这个地方的那个火炬手一样，想要摧毁他的敌人。那么......你想要摧毁谁？
