Toph,"No! Stop sinking! No! I'm sorry, Appa.",没有！停止下沉！没有！对不起，阿帕。
Wan Shi Tong,At least I'll have one specimen to add to my collection.,至少我会有一个标本添加到我的收藏中。
Wan Shi Tong,"Your waterbending won't do you much good here. I've studied Northern water style, Southern water style, even Foggy Swamp style.",你的饮水不会对你有好处。我研究过北方水风，南方水风，甚至是雾沼泽风格。
Sokka,That's called Sokka style. Learn it.,这就是所谓的Sokka风格。学习它。
Sokka,"Wait! Professor, let's go.",等待！教授，我们走吧。
